  <brief_title>The Effect of Ivabradine on Patients With Postural Tachycardia Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of &quot;Funny&quot; Channel Blocker Ivabradine on Patients With Postural Tachycardia Syndrome.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
